Enum MessageType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<MessageType>
      • commInfra.MessageType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<MessageType>

    public enum MessageType
extends java.lang.Enum<MessageType>
    MessageType is an enumeration of all the message types that can be exchanged between the entities.
